prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D illustration for a greeting card front. In a dreamy fantasy art style, depict cartoon versions of Lao Lao and Jordan from the provided photo, maintaining their respective clothing but with any logos or text removed. The setting is a magical, surreal beach under a soft twilight sky with swirling pastel clouds in shades of lavender, peach, and soft pink.

In a humorous and lighthearted scene, Lao Lao and Jordan are comically attempting to build an enormous, wobbly sandcastle that defies gravity. Lao Lao, with a mischievous grin, is precariously perched on Jordan's shoulders, trying to place a magical glowing seashell on the highest turret. Jordan, standing below, has a funny, strained expression as he tries to keep his balance on the sand. The sandcastle itself is fantastical, with spiraling towers, glowing windows, and tiny, funny-looking sand crabs wearing little party hats scurrying around its base. The ocean waves are made of sparkling, iridescent liquid that gently laps at the shore, leaving behind shimmering stardust instead of foam.

In the center of the image, floating softly in the air just below the characters, is the text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao" written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script with a subtle glow. The overall feeling is whimsical, magical, and funny, a perfect blend of a dreamy fantasy world and a playful personal moment.
